wiki.content: Eve, Psyche & The Bluebeard's wife (Korean title: 이브, 프시케 그리고 푸른 수염의 아내) is a song recorded by South Korean girl group LE SSERAFIM for their first full album, UNFORGIVEN. It was released on May 1, 2023, and released as the second single for the album on May 24, 2023 with an official music video. This track was originally teased on the concept trailer for ANTIFRAGILE, with member HUH YUNJIN's written lines, however in that version, it was a rock-inspired track written for the trailer only. The track is a Baltimore Club song, lyrically mainly about wishing for what is forbidden to you. Eve, Psyche & The Bluebeard’s wife are three different mythological figures, all who were curious and looked to what was forbidden to them and would end up in misfortune because of this. LE SSERAFIM includes these characters to represent women disobeying the rules set for them by society, which links to the title of their album “UNFORGIVEN.” The characters mentioned may not be forgiven by some for what they did, but they don’t need to be because the actions caused by their curiosity allowed them to see the truth that was hidden by them.
